---
/**
 * Corporate Compliance Component
 * Purpose: Displays South African corporate compliance metrics and certifications
 * Dependencies: None
 * Structural Role: Compliance disclosure component
 */
---

<section id="corporate-compliance">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Corporate Compliance & Certifications</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-12">Kharon Fire and Security Solutions operates in strict adherence to South African National Standards and corporate regulatory requirements.</p>

    <article id="compliance-saqcc" class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-7 border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">SAQCC Fire Certification</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Our operational capabilities are validated by the South African Qualification and Certification Committee (SAQCC) for the Fire Industry. All field service dispatches are conducted by registered personnel.</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-kharon-blue font-semibold mr-3">•</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="font-bold">SANS 1475 (Fire Extinguishers):</strong> <span class="text-sm px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded ml-2">Verified</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-kharon-blue font-semibold mr-3">•</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="font-bold">SANS 10139 (Fire Detection):</strong> <span class="text-sm px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded ml-2">Verified</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-kharon-blue font-semibold mr-3">•</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="font-bold">SANS 14520 (Gas Suppression):</strong> <span class="text-sm px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded ml-2">Verified</span>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article id="compliance-bbbee" class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-7 border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">B-BBEE Status</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We are a verified Broad-Based Black Economic Empowerment (B-BBEE) contributor. Our current certification supports the procurement requirements of critical infrastructure and enterprise partners.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700"><strong class="font-bold">Current Status:</strong> <span class="font-mono text-kharon-blue">Level 2</span> Contributor</p>
    </article>

    <article id="compliance-paia" class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Promotion of Access to Information Act (PAIA)</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">In compliance with Section 51 of the Promotion of Access to Information Act (No. 2 of 2000), our PAIA Manual is available for public record and outlines the procedures for requesting access to organizational records.</p>
      <a 
        href="/legal/paia-manual.pdf" 
        target="_blank" 
        rel="noopener noreferrer" 
        download
        class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-kharon-blue hover:bg-kharon-purple text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition duration-300"
      >
        Download PAIA Manual (PDF)
        <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
